<p class="header noPspace" dir="ltr">Spring Healing Groups</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr"><strong>Below is a list of healing groups coming this Spring. Registration will begin the weekend of April 5-6.</strong></p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr"><strong>BEAUTY FOR ASHES</strong></p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">This group is designed to be a safe place for women seeking emotional healing due to sexual abuse and/or sexual assault. Strict anonymity and confidentiality will be maintained during this 12 week course of up to 15 women.</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr"><strong>GRIEF</strong></p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">For those who have experienced the death of a loved one, and are seeking to understand the pain and disorientation it brings, through a biblical perspective.</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr"><strong>INFERTILITY</strong></p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">Infertility is a group for couples and/ or individuals of all ages and stages of infertility. The group will provide a safe, confidential, supportive and faith-based environment to meet others who are also facing infertility issues.</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr"><strong>RECOVERY AND REDEMPTION</strong></p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">Explore what the bible says about addiction and recovery. You will hear personal stories of struggle and hope, do the 12 steps from a biblical perspective, and receive support.</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr"><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>ONGOING GROUPS</strong></span></p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr"><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr"><strong>HEALING BETRAYED HEARTS</strong></p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">A safe place for women who need support regarding the impact of a spouse or partner&rsquo;s struggle with pornography or inappropriate sexual behavior.</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr"><strong>MEN&rsquo;S HEALTHY CHOICES</strong></p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">If you&rsquo;re struggling with any type of addiction, from alcohol to food, and you&rsquo;re ready to do something about it, come as you are and learn how to overcome those addictions in a safe environment.</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr"><strong>MEN&rsquo;S HEALTHY SEXUALITY</strong></p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">Join this group of men who are living lives free of pornography and other destructive behaviors. You are not alone. You need not be hopeless. Gain freedom.</p>
<div>&nbsp;</div>